description:
In this special crossover movie event that's fun for the whole family, Twilight Sparkle and her pony friends Pinkie Pie, Rainbow Dash, Applejack, Rarity, and Fluttershy appear at the doorstep of Sonic the Hedgehog, seeking help. Their world of Equestria is on the brink of destruction and only Sonic's boyfriend Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin can save it. 

Starring all your favorite wacky characters like Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin, his personal bitch, and many more.
